## IMPORTANT NOTES

Render free tier:
- The backend "sleeps" after 15 minutes with no traffic
- First request after sleep takes ~30 seconds (cold start)
- This is normal — just wait a moment on first load
- 750 free hours/month = enough for one always-on service

ngrok free tier:
- URL changes every time you restart the Colab session
- Always re-run Step 2 after restarting Colab
- Keep the Colab tab open — it disconnects if the browser tab closes

Google Colab free:
- T4 GPU — fast enough for all features
- Sessions last up to 12 hours
- If Colab disconnects: re-run all cells → re-register URL (Step 2)
- Models load from Google Drive — fast after first load (~2 min)

