```

Then register Colab URL to localhost as before:
```powershell
Invoke-WebRequest -Uri "http://localhost:5000/set-colab-url" -Method POST `
  -ContentType "application/json" `
  -Body '{"url": "https://YOUR-NGROK-URL.ngrok-free.app"}'
```

