## TROUBLESHOOTING

App shows "Offline" (red dot):
→ Render backend may be sleeping — wait 30s and refresh
→ Check https://interior-ai-backend.onrender.com/health in browser

App shows "Partial" (yellow dot):
→ Render is running but Colab is not connected
→ Start Colab and run Step 2

Generation fails / times out:
→ Check that Colab Flask cell is still running (cell 13)
→ Re-run Colab Flask cell → re-register URL

Vercel build fails:
→ Make sure REACT_APP_API_URL is set in Vercel env vars
→ Trigger redeploy after adding env var
